high_descs: Walk straight through the kitchen to the white kitchen table at the far end of the room.  Stand facing the white table with a kitchen counter right behind you and the wall on your immediate right.
Pick up the knife with the wooden handle that is at the back right edge of the table, the one behind and to the right of the brown bowl.
Turn left and walk a few steps, then turn left and walk back through the kitchen (towards the door) to the fridge on the right hand side.  Face the fridge.
Open the fridge door (bottom door), slice half of the potato on the top shelf on the right hand side, then close the fridge door, leaving the potato inside.
Turn right and walk past the sink and counter (on the left).  Once at the end of the counter, turn around to face the trash can and short end of the counter where the toaster sits.
Stick the knife, blade side down, into the silver plate that sits on the counter in front of the toaster.
Walk back along the counter, past the sink on your right, to the fridge.  Face the fridge.
Open the fridge door (bottom door), take out one slice of potato from the top shelf, then close the fridge door.

Holding the potato slice, turn right and walk past the sink and counter (on the left).  Once at the end of the counter, turn around to face the trash can and short end of the counter where the toaster sits.
Put the potato slice behind the knife on the silver plate.
Pick up the plate with the potato slice and knife on it.
Walk past the counter and sink on your right to the fridge. Face the fridge.
Open the bottom fridge door and place the plate with the knife and potato slice on the top shelf, on the left hand side. Close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Place a silver plate with a knife and potato slice on it into the fridge.

turn right and move towards the wall, then turn left  and move forward slightly, then turn left and face the trash can that's sitting below the end of the counter with the plate on it

open the refrigerator, take out a slice of the cut potato, then close the refrigerator

open the refrigerator and put the plate, potato slice, and knife into the refrigerator, then close the refrigerator
